          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 22</h1><p><strong>Questions 1 - 5</strong></p><p>Choose the correct letter, <strong>A, B or C</strong>.</p><p>1 On what date and at what time does Max and John’s plane leave?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    24th August at 7.30 p.m.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    6th September at 5 p.m.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    24th August at 5 p.m.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>2 At which airport does Max and John’s plane arrive?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    JFK</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    Newark</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    La Guardia</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>3 How will Max and John travel into the city from the airport?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    By subway</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    By bus</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    By taxi</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>4 At which hotel do Max and John decide to stay?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    The Grand Hotel</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    The Garden Hotel</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    The Central Motel</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>5 What room and breakfast arrangements do Max and John agree to book?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    Two single rooms with breakfast</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    Two single rooms without breakfast</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    Twin room without breakfast</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>",
